"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178840/extras/10f8f728661d77ec971aa853a4b88202.poster.avif?t=1754557593\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178840/extras/10f8f728661d77ec971aa853a4b88202.webm?t=1754557593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178840/extras/10f8f728661d77ec971aa853a4b88202.mp4?t=1754557593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >任务控制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演 <strong>Yang Sungbin</strong>。尽管肉眼无法看到怪物，但监控摄像头却能发现它的位置。控制这些摄像头，帮助其他玩家安全驾驶飞船。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178840/extras/7d48305486a7effca1112ff8761ac41d.poster.avif?t=1754557593\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178840/extras/7d48305486a7effca1112ff8761ac41d.webm?t=1754557593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178840/extras/7d48305486a7effca1112ff8761ac41d.mp4?t=1754557593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合作社面临的挑战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解决各种合作迷你游戏。没有一个游戏可以单独完成，每个游戏都需要您与其他玩家通力合作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>本项目的灵感来自 <strong>A Way Out</strong> 和 <strong>Keep Talking and Nobody Explodes</strong> 等游戏。</i></p>",
